 halftone grids), fine sand-like noise within all color fills simulating Grain Touch screening mode, organic ink density variations creating tonal shifts without smooth gradients, slight dot gain effect at color boundaries, and spot color separation logic with translucent ink layering behavior rather than CMYK process colors. Colors must be bold, flat, vibrant, and fully saturated (80-100% chroma) with maximum brightness, utilizing fluorescent ink vibrancy where appropriate and showing no fading, desaturation, or washed-out pastels. The border design should use a maximum of 3-4 spot colors plus black, with the character surrounded by a thick uniform black outline (3-4pt stroke weight). Background within the border should be cream/off-white (#FFF8E7) to simulate aged tarot card stock. The output must be 3000×5200px resolution in sRGB, containing absolutely no text labels, character names, tarot card titles, zodiac symbols (♈♉♊♋♌♍♎♏♐♑♒♓), Roman numerals, descriptive typography, or dimensional effects like drop shadows.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-9V68nX0AAHE3P.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-uNF-ZXQAAKbIH.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/promptprincess/status/2012922582299713823", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-18T16:18:36.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"\u2729 em \u2729\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/promptprincess\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
