The lighting across all four frames is consistent: a powerful key light from the side mimicking sunset, soft fill lighting to maintain detail in the shadows, and high-contrast color grading that makes the yellow saree pop against the moody, dark green and grey tones of the environment. The overall atmosphere is intimate, sensual, and sophisticated.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G-zjEn5b0AAIVaa.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/AIRevSpot/status/2012232811273667043", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-16T18:37:42.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"QuestGlitch\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/AIRevSpot\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
